===Higher eduction===
The city of Valence is now developing its high level educational role in the Dr<U+00F4>me/[[Ard<U+00E8>che]] area with one [[Institut National Polytechnique de Grenoble|INPG]] engineering school ([[ESISAR]]), one [[Institut universitaire de technologie]] (IUT) and annexes of three universities (UPMF, [[Universit<U+00E9> Joseph Fourier|UJF]], [[Stendhal University|Stendhal]]). Many other and more specialized schools are also located in Valence.

*[[Joseph Fourier University]]: science, technology, health, STAPS, {{Interlanguage link|fr|<U+00C9>cole sup<U+00E9>rieure du professorat et de l'<U+00E9>ducation|<U+00C9>cole sup<U+00E9>rieure du professorat et de l'<U+00E9>ducation|ESPE}}
