===Employment===
In 2009, 44,612 people had a job, of which 91.4% was salaried employment. The rate of unemployment in the city is 16.5%.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.insee.fr/fr/bases-de-donnees/esl/comparateur.asp?codgeo=COM-26362|title=Emploi sur la commune}}</ref>

